name: The Fool
description: Card #1 in a series of 22 FullMoonTarot Major Arcana. On the eve of each full moon, 3 of 22 Major Arcana cards are drawn IRL from a standard tarot deck. Wallets that match all 3 with FullMoonTarot versions win a new FMT Minor Arcana card with edition size limited to # of winners. Additional surprise draws to be announced during each waxing moon. All cards have future utility. Winning cards must be evident in wallet 2 hrs prior to draw for valid win. Must DM Twitter with request to receive your airdrop win! DM Twitter with questions @fomoboy3
